Lena
Text: Weren't you going to pursue your justice? Weren't you... going to end this darkness?!

Name: Lena
Text: You have to get away from here. You... have to get away!
What in the world is going on?!
"Captain, there was an unidentified explosion at the lab!"
Squad 1 is setting off for investigation!
Cause has not been confirmed yet!
Emergency landing of the rear flying fortress!
Retreat back to the safe passage!
Squad 1 ready to attack the intruders!

Name: Echo
Text: "Lena said there's a commotion in the labs, so not as many guards are pursuing us."

Name: Echo
Text: Now's the best chance to leave.

Name: Echo
Text: "This is the first time we have fought together, isn't it..."

Name: Echo
Text: "I trust that you have my back, Cecily!"

Name: Echo
Text: I will show no mercy this time!

Name: Base Guard
Text: What a shitty job to watch the test subject.

Name: Base Guard
Text: Coming back here at a time like this...

Name: Base Guard
Text: I'll have someone else to do this next time... Hmm?

Name: Lena            In Call
Text: "Alisa, the area around the lab is a mess... Listen to me, we don't have much time left."

Name: Lena            In Call
Text: You need to get your armor and get out of here following the path we discussed before.

Name: Lena            In Call
Text: "From this platform, you can jump to the area between the two shields."

Name: Lena            In Call
Text: "To catch you, they will have to shut down the shields, and you can take the opportunity to break the siege."

Name: Lena            In Call
Text: We don't have much time... Hurry!

Name: Lena            In Call
Text: Tsk... They are coming back! Careful!
The flying fortress has taken off!
Watch out for the test subject!
This won't work. She will destroy the flying fortress...

Name: Echo
Text: Time to wake up from this... empty dream!

Name: Echo
Text: This is bad. It's that Aurora Bastion with M.I.N.D. disruptor...

Name: Echo
Text: "Are you ready! Here we go, Cecily!"

Name: Aurora Captain
Text: Utopia is the best place to be!

Name: Aurora Captain
Text: "Long time no see, you've improved a lot, Alisa."

Name: Aurora Captain
Text: Squad 2! Get transport vehicles ready for support!

Name: α
Text: "If you want to have a more direct ""communication,"" I'm here for it!"
This is the best you can do?
Life and death are but a moment apart…

Name: Lucia
Text: This game... It's hard to say what will happen next.

Name: Lucia
Text: Though I want to give Commandant some advice...

Name: Lucia
Text: It seems... I can't contact Commandant from here...

Name: Lucia
Text: But we still have the M.I.N.D. connection.

Name: Lucia
Text: The only thing I can do is to trust Commandant's judgment.

Name: Lucia
Text: Looks like it's my turn now.

Name: Lucia
Text: BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER... She's ahead of me.

Name: Lucia
Text: ...I have to catch up with her.

Name: Lucia
Text: I wonder what the game looks like after modification.

Name: Lucia
Text: "Anyway, move to the designated position first."

Name: Lucia
Text: All those enemies just now are from our world...
We should still proceed with caution.

Name: Lucia
Text: The Red Tide...? BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER... Watch out!

Name: Qu
Text: Are they here already? Evacuate the civilians.

Name: Qu
Text: I won't let you ravage this place.

Name: Qu
Text: Go back and take care of the injured with Tai'E.

Name: Qu
Text: Fall back now. We must not give Tabula Akasha and Huaxu more stress.

Name: Qu
Text: The Corrupted Soldiers above us are too dangerous. I'll take care of them.

Name: "Bai Gui, Chiwen Crew"
Text: "Lady Qu, those Babylonians will be here soon."

Name: Qu
Text: Get the central control room ready...

Name: Qu
Text: It's a matter of time before this place is set on fire.

Name: Qu
Text: Proceed with caution when you deal with the outsiders.

Name: Qu
Text: These weapons for Tabula Akasha's defense must be destroyed as they've been corrupted.

Name: Qu
Text: The ground's shaking... What's going on?!

Name: Kowloong Civilian
Text: I should have just stayed up there!

Name: Lucia
Text: "I can't let them do that, no matter what it takes..."

Name: Lucia
Text: Inside these porcelain-textured Corrupted are all mechanical devices.

Name: Chrome
Text: They have been getting even crazier since just now.

Name: Wanshi
Text: Feels like there's someone around... Who's there?
What's going on with these things?!
Their number has been growing since just now.

Name: Chrome (in Communication)
Text: "According to the plan Commandant had before falling unconscious, we can't stay here any longer."

Name: Chrome (in Communication)
Text: Separate and break through the enemy lines. Strike Hawk's mission is completed. We will be right there.

Name: Wanshi (in Communication)
Text: "Leave the rest to the Engineering Force, Captain."
<color=#D1D1D1><size=35>Tabula Akasha</size></color>\n<size=28>Mission target: Break through the enemies.</size>\n<size=28>Huaxu's computing core is damaged.</size>

Name: Pulao?
Text: "Hi, Lady Qu. I'm preparing meals for the Pulao Crew."

Name: Pulao?
Text: Would you like to taste it?

Name: Qu
Text: Is this a... consciousness data fragment?

Name: Qu
Text: But it doesn't look like any data saved in Tabula Akasha.

Name: Qu
Text: This... is still the same battlefield.

Name: Qu
Text: How long has it been? I have lost track of time.

Name: Qu
Text: These people... Did they all die in war?

Name: Qu
Text: "No, Tabula Akasha shouldn't have such memory records!"

Name: Qu
Text: "Fight, until we no longer have to!"
